Bank of Italy sets 15 . 0 trillion lire repo tender . The Bank of Italy said it called a 15 . 0 trillion lire repurchase tender for today or Thursday for government securities to be resold on August 1 . At the previous comparable operation for 5 . 0 trillion lire on June 24 , the minimum accepted rate stood at 6 . 90 percent and the average rate at 6 . 93 percent . 
